oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Spain
beach regeneration
Villajoyosa Beach
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: In the last two years a whole of studies was realized in order to determine precise solutions to the regeneration of Villajoyosa's beach, in the Spanish mediterranean coast. Investigations were carried out to the surrounding coastal areas based in field investigations and laboratory analyses of the beaches materials.
